# Lists & Content

**Figma:** [Lists](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=7641-2142&p=f&m=dev)

List structure, rows, dividers, and placeholders below are derived from Figma component library node 7641:2142.

---

## Variables (from design-system-tokens.mdc)

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Row bg | `--bg-base-default` or `--bg-base-secondary` |
| Divider | `--border-base-default` |
| Placeholder | `--bg-base-tertiary` |

---

## Structure

### List items
- **Background:** `--bg-base-default` or `--bg-base-secondary`.
- **Padding:** Space/200–300.

### Dividers
- **Style:** `--border-base-default` 1px.

### Image/media placeholders
- **Fill:** `--bg-base-tertiary`.

---

## Spacing

- Consistent Space scale (4, 8, 12, 16, 24) for gaps and padding.

---

## Implementation guidelines

- Use tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc` only.
- Do not invent variants; implement only what exists in Figma node 7641:2142.
